public interface MolecularChargeService<I extends Identifier>
extends QueryService<I>

MolecularChargeService - 28.02.2012

Defines a service that can look-up charge on an given identifier. There is currently no support for searching charge as the results sets would likely be very large. If a specific charge is required one approach could be to search with a different criteria (i.e. molecular formula) and then filter those results for the desired charge

Double getCharge(I identifier)
Look-up the charge value for a given identifier. If no charge is found then Double.NAN is returned.

Parameters:
identifier - query identifier
Returns:
the charge of the identifier, Double.NAN if no charge is found.
